# TrashAdvisor

Docker version in progress

On linux, run the following command

```
git clone https://github.com/MEEM-MLHD/trashadvisor
cd trashadvisor
docker-compose up
```

On OSX, run the following command

First time:

```
docker-machine create --driver virtualbox --virtualbox-memory 8096 trashadvisor
```

```
git clone https://github.com/MEEM-MLHD/trashadvisor
cd trashadvisor
docker-machine start trashadvisor
eval "$(docker-machine env trashadvisor)"
docker-machine ip trashadvisor
docker-compose up
```

Feed the db with initial data

```
docker-compose run db bash
/etc/init.d/mysql start
mysql -u root -p123456
create database myapp
mysql -u root -p123456 myapp < /src/data/trashadvisor.php
```


```
eval "$(docker-machine env brahms)"
docker-compose run db /srv/data/restore_db.sh
```
